<p class="style1">PurchaseBeverage Acceptance Test</p>

<p class="style1">The user will not be able to purchase a beverage if they do not deposit enough money into the CoffeeMaker. Change will be dispensed to the user, if they paid more than the price of the beverage. A user&#39;s money will be returned if there is not enough inventory to make the beverage.</p>

<p class="style1">There are 3 recipes in the CoffeeMaker: Coffee,50,6,1,1,0; Latte, 75,6,6,0,0; and Hot Chocolate,100,0,2,0,2</p>

